Newsletter Export is a Drupal module which allows a specific node type
to be exported as raw HTML. This is excellent for building a node type
to use as a newsletter. A template file is provided to allow you to completely
customize the output of your fields.

Template File: 
newsletter-export.tpl.php

provides three variables

$raw_markup -> The raw markup that drupal would provide for your node
$fields -> An array of all the fields and their values
$node -> The entire node object
